391
00:26:00,196 --> 00:26:01,208
Butterflies!

392
00:26:05,595 --> 00:26:07,355
Butterflies!

393
00:26:07,796 --> 00:26:10,235
So many butterflies!

394
00:26:37,436 --> 00:26:39,076
Jinzhao, look, butterfly.

395
00:26:43,835 --> 00:26:44,796
You are so bad.

396
00:26:44,796 --> 00:26:46,235
