417
00:28:27,676 --> 00:28:28,956
or someone else?

418
00:28:31,875 --> 00:28:32,984
You're Jinzhao.

419
00:28:42,916 --> 00:28:43,556
What's wrong?

420
00:28:44,276 --> 00:28:44,796
Nothing.

421
00:28:47,352 --> 00:28:49,515
