543
00:36:45,436 --> 00:36:45,795
Let's go.

544
00:36:51,875 --> 00:36:53,236
Qi, stop watching.

545
00:36:53,676 --> 00:36:54,996
If it's really related to our origins,

546
00:36:55,075 --> 00:36:56,236
